profile:
Real Estate Movers, with over 9 years of experience our crews will show you how we take pride in what we do every day. No move is to BIG or to SMALL, Real Estate Movers does it all! We offer competitively hourly rates in Calgary and flat rates on long distance moves across AB, BC, and SK. Customer satisfaction guaranteed! 

Locally operated in Alberta - Now offering Long Distance Moving Services across Canada.
services: From your first contact with our owner Victor Rusu, you'll be at ease from the knowledge and understanding of our courteous and professional staff. We are a fit and energetic group, ready to get the job done. All of our movers are professional and non smokers. What sets us apart from other movers is the fact we are an owner operated company, which means the owner is ALWAYS on the job. Our movers will take time to make sure they get the job done to your satisfaction. Call us and discover how stress free moving can be!
specialities:
Packing and Unpacking services 
Assembly and Take Down
Out/to storage moves 
Staging 
Office moves 
Piano moves 
Deliveries 
Long distance moves: AB,BC,SK.
Residential, Commercial & Office moves.
